#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (KMessageWidget, kmessagewidget)
#: kcmqtquicksettingswidget.ui:23
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"These settings adjust the QtQuick settings used by Plasma. Modifying these "
"settings can break your desktop. Only adjust these settings if you know what "
"you are doing."
msgstr ""
"Tsia-ê siat-tīng ē kái Plasma iōng ê QtQuick siat-tīng. Kái tsia-ê siat-tīng "
"khó-lîng ē hāi lí ê toh-bīn pháinn-khì. Nā lí m̄-tsai-iánn kái tsia-ê siat-"
"tīng ē ū siánn-mih hāu-kó, tiō tshiánn mài kái tsia-ê siat-tīng."

